short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Embed internal MDCU links into pubmed articles.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Instantly access full-text articles from MDCU library with FindIt@Chula for PubMed! This Google Chrome extension adds a direct link to the internal MDCU system, seamlessly connecting you to full-text papers while browsing PubMed article pages.

By integrating FindIt@Chula within PubMed, users can enjoy a streamlined research experience and effortlessly access Chulalongkorn University's vast library resources. Stay focused on your research and save time with FindIt@Chula for PubMed!
